vstore.framework.error.events

Class ErrorEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • vstore.framework.error.events.ErrorEvent

  • public class ErrorEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    This event gets published if an error in the Framework occurred. The different error codes are listed in the enum ErrorCode.
